data.description: Show stopper in Sapphire Pointe!!! OVER 5,000 FINISHED SQ FT!! Fully-furnished home, to make it a hassle free move in experience!! Make this dream home yours today! 3 Car Garage! Cul de sac! Finished basement with movie theater!!! 5 bedrooms plus 2nd floor loft. Brand new concrete driveway and steps!! Covered front porch, covered back patio and fire pit!!2-story formal living room, open floor plan formal living and dining, kitchen and great room. Gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, double oven, kitchen island, granite countertops, bar seating, bay windows, sliding glass doors out to the quiet and private backyard oasis!!! Great room with carpet flooring and ceiling fan, awesome feature of a double sided gas fireplace in the great room and main floor bedroom!!! Main floor bedroom currently being used as home office. Upstairs, you will find 2 secondary bedrooms with a jack and jill bathroom and walk in closets. PLUS, an extra full bathroom in the hallway so no one has to share! Second floor loft great for second home office space! The second floor primary suite is absolutely stunning. Get cozy by the fireplace reading a book or magazine or scrolling on your phone with your morning coffee. Vaulted ceilings, en suite 5 piece bathroom with walk through walk in closet!!! Must check that out!! Not to be outdone, the finished basement is complete with a home theater system, additional family room, wet bar, 3/4 hallway bathroom with gorgeous modern finishes, and a private guest suite with en suite 3/4 bathroom!!! Backs to greenbelt, open space backing to Diamond Ridge Estates! Enjoy outdoor pools, trails, parks, pickle, basketball and tennis courts! Minutes from Downtown Castle Rock, Castle Rock Outlets, Sams Club, Whole Foods, La Loma, Los Dos Potrillos, Home Goods/TJ Maxx, and MORE!!!! http://www.1062titanite.com/
